            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Clear Daily Soothing UV Defense SPF</strong><br>
                Protect your skin from harmful UV rays with this lightweight, calming sunscreen. It hydrates without
                clogging pores and shields sensitive areas from sun-induced redness and inflammation—keeping your
