              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto A+ Brightening Treatment Serum</strong><br>
                This lightweight, oil-free serum visibly reduces redness and blotchiness while smoothing skin texture.
                Packed with azelaic acid and other botanical actives, it calms irritated skin and promotes an even skin
