              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Gel</strong><br>
                Instantly soothe sensitive skin with this calming botanical gel. Enriched with hyaluronic acid,
                cucumber, and thyme, it provides a cooling sensation while reducing visible redness and supporting
                hydration.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Essence Mist</strong><br>
                Refresh and calm your skin anytime throughout the day with this lightweight mist. Designed to reduce
                visible redness and strengthen the skin barrier, it’s perfect for on-the-go soothing and hydration.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Redness Neutralizer</strong><br>
                Finish your routine with this advanced redness-reducing treatment. Formulated with biomimetic peptides and natural extracts, it strengthens the skin’s resistance to triggers of inflammation and helps maintain long-term calmness and comfort.
